Fernando Munoz Bernal is a Colombian who has been in China for more thanÂ 20 years. He keeps sharing his China experience on social media. In this video, he recalls how he witnessed the poverty alleviation and common prosperity policies have changed China in the past 20 years, including infrastructure construction, eco-tourism projects, telemedicine in remote areas, and more. "China's poverty alleviation success is the most significant humanitarian achievement in the history of the world," said Fernando Munoz Bernal.